      "description": "This car is in poor condition. It has significant mechanical issues and will likely require repairs to run reliably. The interior and exterior show considerable wear, including visible damage to the body, upholstery, and trim. This vehicle is best suited for someone willing to invest in repairs or looking for a parts car.",
